# WATCHR MOBILE - React Native + Expo

Framework: React Native + Expo (TypeScript)
Navigation: @react-navigation/bottom-tabs (4 tabs)
API base: EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL

# Design tokens (src/theme/tokens.ts)
Colors.bg:#07090d bg1:#0c1018 bg2:#111621 bg3:#161d2c
Colors.line:#1e2840 line2:#283350
Colors.t0:#e8edf8 t1:#9aabc8 t2:#4d6082 t3:#2a3a58
Colors.up:#ff3b47 Colors.dn:#2b7fff Colors.amber:#f5a623 Colors.teal:#00d4aa
FontFamily.mono: IBM_Plex_Mono
FontFamily.sans: NotoSansKR

# Rules
- Use StyleSheet.create
- Import and use only token colors
- Price/number text should prefer mono family
- Storage keys must use sm_ prefix
- Polling logic should clean up intervals on unmount
